scenes.title: equal radii
scenes.content:
The two selected pink struts prove that the vertices are the same distance from the origin. 

The unselected pink strut is coincidentally the same length.

The white struts are all the same length.
The blue struts are all the same length.
The peach struts are all the same length.

The peach struts are NOT the same length as the blue struts, so the quadrilateral sides are not exactly rectangles as they should be for a true gyrobicupola.
